      <title>莱恩表示，欧洲央行并未预先承诺特定的利率路径</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/ecb-isn-t-pre-committing-to-a-particular-rate-path-lane-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行首席经济学家菲利普·莱恩表示，欧洲央行正在采取逐次会议的方式制定下一步货币政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/ecb-isn-t-pre-committing-to-a-particular-rate-path-lane-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 20:42:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Block 将把 10% 的比特币利润转化为比特币投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/block-to-flip-10-of-bitcoin-profit-into-bitcoin-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Block Inc. 上调了全年利润指引，并透露计划将比特币的部分利润重新投入到比特币资产中，杰克·多尔西 (Jack Dorsey) 的公司对比特币的未来下了很大的赌注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/block-to-flip-10-of-bitcoin-profit-into-bitcoin-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 20:17:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
